01:11:28,340 --> 01:11:31,760
[SPEAKER_01] O da, super, evo.

692
01:11:31,760 --> 01:11:33,380
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, je baš super knjigo.

693
01:11:33,380 --> 01:11:34,380
