[SPEAKER_00] Snaga u nama.

695
01:11:37,300 --> 01:11:39,579
[SPEAKER_00] Očito, tu ti još nisam došao.

696
01:11:39,579 --> 01:11:41,100
[SPEAKER_00] Biti iskren tijema sebi.

697
01:11:41,100 --> 01:11:42,779
[SPEAKER_01] Da, vidi ovo, čovječe.

698
01:11:42,779 --> 01:11:44,659
[SPEAKER_01] Razlog za sreću.

699
01:11:44,659 --> 01:11:46,840
[SPEAKER_01] Biti jače, ozlo pamteno sebi.

700
01:11:46,840 --> 01:11:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] A, ovo.

701
01:11:47,380 --> 01:11:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] A mislim, on je to napisao kako se zove, baš ono sve po učenju Viktora Frankola.

702
01:11:53,619 --> 01:11:54,439
