745
01:16:38,159 --> 01:16:39,600
[SPEAKER_02] Kak ćeš doći do tamo?

746
01:16:39,600 --> 01:16:43,220
[SPEAKER_02] Hoćeš sjesti u auto, pa krenut?

747
01:16:43,220 --> 01:17:03,300
